title: June 24: In Any World (Chapter Thirteen)
body:
Explicit

Tags: Alternative Universes, universe hopping, friends to lovers, fanfiction, getting together

Summary:  Returning home after his second world tour, Dan feels lost, bored, and without direction. But things are about to get much more exciting when, while reading fanfiction in the bath,  Dan slips, hits his head, and passes out. When he wakes up, it’s to a world that definitely isn’t the one he came from, especially because his best friend is in bed with him. And if he thinks that is strange, things are about to get a whole lot weirder.

Tags for this chapter: Manchester, breakfast bar

tags: I just rewatched it last night
summary: the final google feud video is quintessential dnp content tbh. if you want to get a feel of what their dynamic is like, watch...
body: the final google feud video is quintessential dnp content tbh. if you want to get a feel of what their dynamic is like, watch that video. you get it all: dan being obnoxious, phil being stressed out, both talking incomprehensible shit that only they understand, phil sponning his merch, weird intense flirting that makes you feel like a third wheel but also like you’re watching some kind of strange mating ritual of some rare species?? there is a random pizza interlude, an analysis of what would happen if robots replaced humans, an intro that is way too long because they get lost in their own rambling and end up talking too much, a brief moment of synchronized singing, phil lester’s iconic “I don’t have legs” line and more. they must have been on some kind of sugar high because it’s all especially dramatic and loud. it’s a wild ride, please watch it.

Our goal is to create an alphabetized library of every phanfiction in the phandom. Besides that, we compile masterlists of different genres that are scheduled for posting every few days, and help find fics that have been mislocated.

title: PWP (5) Masterlist
body:
part one part two, part three, part four

A YouTuber and a Raptor Trainer Walk into a Bar (ao3) - Allthephils

Summary: Dan and Phil made an agreement that they got a free pass to hookup with their celebrity crushes if the opportunity ever arose. Here’s what happened when it did.

dark purple sky (darkness comes out to play) (ao3) - knlalla

Summary: the one where Dan gets a blowjob from a complete stranger in the middle of the forest on Halloween.

dipping in (ao3) - jestbee

Summary: “So many dips,” Phil says. “You’ll never use them all.”

“Wanna bet?”

Double Ended - auroraphilealis

Summary: Dan and Phil play with a double ended Dildo.

fringe check (ao3) - CoffinWeaver (politely_ironic)

Summary: phil has some feelings about his hair. dan does too. these are vastly different emotions.

Hippo Milk Is Actually Pink (ao3) - deletable_bird

Summary: In Which Dan Is Drunk, Phil Is Also Drunk, They Hook Up, And Things Just Kind Of Go From There.

hot dog, I sure am glad to see ya! (ao3) - theprincessed

Summary: The Mickey Mouse room in Florida sees some unexpected action…

Innocence - yiffandquiff

Summary: Dan was always adamant about not having sex before marriage. But one day he decides he wants to try it with his boyfriend, Phil. But he has one condition: he doesn’t want to see Phil’s dick during sex.

i’m exactly where you like me (ao3) - cosmicphan

Summary: Dan and Phil meet in a gay bar. They fuck.

I’ve got you memorized (ao3) - t_hens

Summary: strip scrabble.

Let’s Party - yiffandquiff

Summary: A party that Phil doesn’t want to go to? check. A night of surprises? also check. And finding unexpected feelings for a friend? Triple check.

Perspective (ao3) - intoapuddle

Summary: Dan has a few tricks that make him look at life from a different perspective, but only a few of them work. Playing around with Phil is one trick that never fails.

Photoshoot - auroraphilealis

Summary: Seeing Dan model his clothing for the new AmazingPhil merch proves to be too much for Phil, who can’t quite bring himself to care that they’re in public.

Properly - knlalla

Summary: Dan’s been trying to take advantage of the all-hours pool for a late night swim, but some guy always shows up before him.

Silk - intoapuddle

Summary: There’s something vulnerable in pushing Dan’s eyes closed, and for some reason Phil can’t stop thinking about it (kink discovery, blindfolded)

Spice (ao3) - whisksandplungers

Summary: Inspired by that bit in the Halloween baking video where Phil says ‘I like it’ and looks at Dan like he is ready to devour him. PWP basically.

Talk Like That - intoapuddle

Summary: Tenderness has its place. But sometimes, even on an evening that is as quiet and unassuming as this one, Phil wants filthy heat and tension that doesn’t require an afterthought.

Under you control(ler) (ao3) - DrunkerWhalers

Summary: Dan was tired of Phil ignoring him for Fortnite so he takes matters into his own hands (well, his mouth at least).
